		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/30/today-in-small-business-my-idea-is-just-too-far-ahead-of-its-time/" data-title="Today in Small Business: &#8216;My Idea Is Just Too Far Ahead of Its Time&#8217;" data-description="How to fire someone without getting sued. Are health care costs growing again?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The winter <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/4/30/5667806/why-economic-growth-ground-to-a-halt-last-quarter">crushed the economy</a> in the first quarter.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ ADP says the <a href="//www.adpemploymentreport.com/">private sector added 220,000 jobs</a> in April.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ And the &#8220;<a href="//www.middlemarketcenter.org/performance-data-on-the-middle-market">middle market</a>&#8221; is projecting growth.</p>
